    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええと、独創的な泳ぎ方でしたね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ that was a very unique way of swimming…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6310869934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.1903167648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "何を焦っていたのか知りませんが\n少しは泳げばいいのにと言ったのは、貴方でしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know why you were so panicked‚\nbut you're the one who told me to swim a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6682262977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.8650106671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに、泳いだら泳いだで文句を言うなんて\nせめて指示は一本化していただけませんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yet when I do swim‚ you complain.\nCould you at least give consistent instructions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0015596311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、悲鳴が聞こえたもので俺も驚いて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I heard a scream‚ so I was surprised…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7751466355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.3393423161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "気のせいでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It must have been your imagination.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3393423161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.0091795008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、凄い慌てた様子でしたよね！？\nあれで、何もなかったことはないと思うんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ you were in a real panic‚ right!?\nI don't think that was nothing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6669587641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.8950533272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "何もないと言ったらないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I say it was nothing‚ it was nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8950533272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.9350505155
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "海でも泳ぎましたし、そろそろ着替えて戻ります\n貴方もいい加減、仕事を片付けた方がいいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've swum in the sea‚ so I'll change and head back.\nYou should finish your work as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7248675744,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7866.6708151000075,
          "startTime": 92.5915383895
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "明日の収録、寝坊しないで下さいね\nそれでは",
